{"tid":116721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[露宿不孤獨！]露宿比住劏房好！","createTime":"2017-02-11T15:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T11:04:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c22345cc9420057191df0995891f533df7ba690f","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"一宿難求，板間房租金更是「吃人」。兼職外判清潔工、53歲的阿奇一直住在板間房，月租2,800元，後來業主重新裝修，要求他搬走。同區一個床位都要月租1,800元，還要一個月上期、一個月按金，加上水電費，實非綜援戶可以承擔，「政府補貼電費都冇用！業主照收！」有腳患的阿奇索性露宿街頭，總比住劏房惹蚤咬好。這是露宿者的「流動」，一時露宿，一時住板間房。但住板間房也不一定比露宿好，所以即使政府如何驅趕，他們最終還是選擇留在街頭。<br />\n<br />\n板間房蚤患嚴重。據他們說，5分鐘上百隻蚤爬滿雙腿。相反在他們管理下，露宿的隧道乾淨企理，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/70738/%E5%85%83%E5%AE%B5%E7%AF%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%B5%E5%AF%92%E9%A2%A8-%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87-%E4%BF%82%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E4%B9%8B%E5%98%9B-%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%83%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F70738%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25AE%25B5%25E7%25AF%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%25AF%2592%25E9%25A2%25A8-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2593%2587-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2598%259B-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2583%25B3&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f8e22e65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/70738/%E5%85%83%E5%AE%B5%E7%AF%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%B5%E5%AF%92%E9%A2%A8-%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87-%E4%BF%82%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E4%B9%8B%E5%98%9B-%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%83%B3</a>"},{"pid":"e039949f9ed9a5753deaad324b9e47aeb15206ac","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/377457/xlarge/8f4b064972fb9e0c24b46d5c7c7692ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F377457%2Fxlarge%2F8f4b064972fb9e0c24b46d5c7c7692ff.jpg&h=78c08e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一間劏房，動輒月租4千大元，對於僅得2千多元綜援的露宿者而言，實在無法負擔。"},{"pid":"97f1ac71ef197666699792ed007818b72b712c4b","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/377455/xlarge/1dbae89e31cf03bc9a1c65cb7b8d6240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F377455%2Fxlarge%2F1dbae89e31cf03bc9a1c65cb7b8d6240.jpg&h=a5ec3063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11a1817fbecd87e42c94e30ec813657abca93fd9","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"強哥做過地盤、廚房，即使身懷手藝也因露宿無地址而令僱主卻步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2558af848bb89cb9e7139bf373a0ee8b2e6103d2","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df21b63e044a7e204dc5fc08b79d268f90335e","tid":116721,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強哥做過地盤、廚房，即使身懷手藝也因露宿無地址而令僱主卻步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以應搞夜市,比個機會佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a94d6a3c3c437bb2b17b46163617e7ee94854b7","tid":116721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}